## Core Capabilities

### NEZA Intent Engine

- **Multimodal ingestion**: Image, text, voice, WhatsApp, Telegram
- **Visual intent extraction**: Product recognition, material detection, quality assessment, style classification (via Vision LLM)
- **Language understanding**: Attribute parsing, urgency detection, preference inference (via LLM Agent)
- **Signal deduplication**: 5-gate logic (technical duplicate, return-after-match, genuine re-submission, velocity flood, default)

### AI Inference Layer (Edge Functions)

- **Image Analysis**: Vision LLM processes uploaded images for product identification
- **Keyword Extraction**: LLM extracts structured attributes from natural language
- **Similarity Scoring**: AI scoring (0-100) per product for match ranking
- **Location Filtering**: City -> country -> global fallback for availability
- **Top-N Ranking**: Returns top 3 matches with confidence thresholds

### EKEX Intelligence Layer

- **Local availability matching**: Real-time stock proximity verification
- **Unmet demand detection**: Classification of unmatched intent for network intelligence
- **Supplier network routing**: Signal distribution to verified supplier pools via WhatsApp/Telegram/Email
- **Regional interoperability**: Cross-city, cross-country demand aggregation
- **Feedback learning**: Temporal decay, confidence adjustment, recursive improvement

---

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend | Vite + React 18 + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui | SPA, mobile-responsive, dark theme |
| Routing | React Router v6 | Client-side navigation |
| State/Data | TanStack Query v5 | Server state management |
| Animation | Framer Motion | UI transitions |
| Backend | Deno Deploy Edge Functions | 20 serverless handlers |
| SDK | @base44/sdk v0.8.25 | Platform integration |
| Database | Base44 Entity DB (document-store) | Primary data store with JSON Schema |
| Mirror DB | Supabase (PostgreSQL) | Secondary analytics store |
| Auth | Base44 Auth + RLS | Identity and access control |
| Email | Resend | Transactional email delivery |
| Notifications | Command Center | Internal webhook routing |
| AI/ML | Vision LLM + LLM Agent | Image analysis, natural language understanding |
| Storage | Base44 File Storage | Image uploads, document storage |
| Realtime | Base44 Realtime | Live signal updates |
| Automations | Base44 Automations | Entity-triggered + scheduled workflows |

