| Name | Type | Trigger | Function |
|---|---|---|---|
| Signal Router | Entity | ConsumerSignal created | routeSignalToSuppliers |
| Supplier Notifier | Entity | ConsumerSignal created | notifySupplierOnSignal |
| App Approved | Entity | SupplierApplication status=approved | notifyCommandCenter |

