## Security

Report vulnerabilities responsibly: [info@ekexintelligence.com](mailto:info@ekexintelligence.com)

**Do NOT open public issues for security vulnerabilities.**

### Security Model

| Layer | Measure |
|---|---|
| Admin access | Identity-locked to single verified email |
| Role hierarchy | super_admin -> operations -> supplier/producer/logistics -> user |
| Frontend guards | useAdminGuard hook on all /admin/* routes |
| Backend guards | Email + role check on every sensitive function |
| Entity RLS | Per-entity create/read/update/delete policies |
| Secrets | All API keys in Deno environment only |

